Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Here at Talisman Saloon, we only discuss the affairs of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Lemonade Candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my friends is in quite a bind right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'd like to talk about her, Talisman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please tell me about the concerns your friend is facing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Talisman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Talisman!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After she graduated from school,\Nshe immediately started a tough job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A job carrying a lot of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she doesn't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.61,0:00:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What she's in a bind about is, I suppose, her work relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At her work, she has this subordinate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.66,0:01:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, a senior colleague...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, she's got this colleague who is hard to describe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no avoiding him when she's at work, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he the sort that she doesn't get along well with?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.88,0:01:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He does some crazy things.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are times that she feels what he's saying is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So she thought she might be able to trust him at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like it might be wishful thinking on your friend's part.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she needs to first discard this preconception and then face his true character.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you give this advice to your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please share with me, Talisman, the difficulties experienced by those adrift.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:02:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is always hiding inside your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Face his true character, huh?
