Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna ask me about Kougami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You two have this strange connection. Almost like fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know how I should deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone told me I should try to understand him better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And someone else told me not to think of him as human like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that must've been Inspector Ginoza.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dogs are dogs. Owners are owners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's where you need to draw the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best if you stay on one side and keep him on the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To understand Kougami means to think the way he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To see the world through his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you do that, your Psycho-Pass will become like his as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"When you gaze long into an abyss, the abyss also gazes into you."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami stared into the darkness for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's still staring into it even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe for him, the only true justice in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.84,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,exists solely in the depths of that darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna go search for something like that with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing more I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop Ko, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunizuka and I are off duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,so go with Kougami and Kagari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The comprehensive home security inspection
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,showed that the toilet in this apartment has been broken for the past two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the resident hasn't filed a single complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So the management company became suspicious and reported it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayama Kimihiko, thirty-two years old. Single. Unemployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Unemployed? Do people like that exist in this day and age?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked his bank account.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's receiving lots of compensation from an affiliated services provider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.27,0:06:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably lived in great comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you can make tons of money just by being popular on the net,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of course you'd feel it's stupid to go outside and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Could he have gone on a trip somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No. When a person leaves their apartment, it leaves a record on the street scanners.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In this town, it's virtually impossible to travel without leaving any trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, his bank account hasn't had any withdrawals for the past two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayama is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Getting killed is easier than disappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too soon to come to a conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible to restart the interior Holo of this room?{doki sucks}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't sit on a Holography couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So normally, the position of the Holo object is synced with the real world one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That couch must've been here originally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But someone moved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've wanted to hide this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother covering such a small scratch?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a Crime Lab Drone scan it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it. Residue from adhesive tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the secret behind the magic trick that they used to make Hayama Kimihiko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,disappear from this place without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He could've been strangled, poisoned, or maybe they stopped his heart with an electric shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, first they killed the victim in some bloodless manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then they spread a plastic sheet over the room and dismantled the body
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,into pieces small enough to fit down the bath or toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayama probably resisted when they tried to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It left a scratch on the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and traces remained of the adhesive tape they used to put down the plastic sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They had the guts and the willpower, but this was the work of amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If old Masaoka were here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd have sniffed out something like this the moment he stepped into the room, Gino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate a hunting dog's sense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the sewer pipe for traces of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can discuss this further after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the avatar that Hayama was using on the net.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He must've been quite popular to have made a living as an affiliate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Talisman...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,met this avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, thanks to the hard work of our precious Crime Lab Drones,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,we successfully found the body pieces that were flushed from Mr. Hayama's residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, applaud!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, someone's operating Hayama's CommuField on the net
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and hanging around using Hayama's avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a horror story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost that remains chained to this world, endlessly wandering the net, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is someone assuming his identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that even before Hayama went missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,he was screwing around using fake IPs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we tried tracking the access routes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can give it a shot, but they're going through proxy servers that are clearly suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're undoubtedly taking steps to hide their tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're not careful, they'll notice we're tracking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But, at least, the person who's using Hayama's avatar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,should still think that they haven't aroused any suspicion yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that give us a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in a sense, the suspect this time isn't hiding or running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but is walking around right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If we play our cards right, we might be able to get him to reveal clues that lead to his real identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's get in touch with Hayama's avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a bad idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But who's gonna do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So this person who's pretending to be Talisman
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,has been operating this CommuField as capably as the real owner for the past two months, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.21,0:10:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him, Inspector Ginoza.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's going to another CommuField.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Let's follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like this is Spooky Boogie's CommuField.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a big community too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.49,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Spooky Boogie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Spooky Boogie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.08,0:11:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The operator of this place is a famous anarchist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If she finds out we're detectives, there might be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she have any connections with Hayama... With Talisman?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, both of them are famous, so she might.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But whether the actual people know each other or not is a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check their access logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If they often visit each other's CommuFields...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Tsunemori?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hm? Inspector Ginoza?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Miss Lemonade Candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Spooky Boogie, the host of this CommuField.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you're quite the unexpected visitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited you to my chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not troubling you, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, not really... But why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors, but you really don't realize how famous you are, do you, Lemonade Candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I call you Miss Tsunemori Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you possibly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you wanna know who I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you look through your graduation album or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you figure it out, I'll treat you at our class reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what business does an Inspector at the CID have with my CommuField?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow I doubt you came just to hang out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you friends with Talisman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, since we're rivals on the access ranking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you noticed anything different lately about his Field or avatar?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, during the past two months?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't you think he was acting strange before then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Around that time, Talisman was speaking erratically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He was also holding events that were clearly intended to get affiliate money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So the number of people who were anti-Talisman was growing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We were saying how it looked like that popular old-timer was on his way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But he isn't like that now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Talisman is his usual cool, gentle self today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Although he said he turned over a new leaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it's quite hard for an avatar who went into decline to make a comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So is this some sort of an investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Talisman do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We still can't say anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but we have to somehow find the actual person using the Talisman avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... That sounds kinda interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I give you a bit of assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be a bad idea to get one of the Public Safety Bureau's rising stars in my debt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Spooky Boogie, the famous anarchist, offering us help?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my public face and this is my private face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We were in the same class, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To those who came to my forum:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.33,0:15:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Spooky Boogie, will hold a modest party to show my appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a meet-up in Roppongi on the 4th,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,where I'll challenge my friend Talisman to a duel for the White Crown I hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A meet-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The users who usually gather in a CommuField on the net
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,hold a party wearing Holo-Cosplay that matches their avatars on the social networks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They sure do come up with strange things these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So are we certain Talisman will participate in the event?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,With things the way they are, his popularity will plummet if he doesn't show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who's pretending to be Hayama Kimihiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,he's been enthusiastic enough about operating the CommuField
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm sure he'll show up there as Talisman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what Holo-Cosplay he's wearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if his Crime Coefficient indicates he's a target for enforcement, the game is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So where will it be held?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be at Exoset, a club in Roppongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginoza and the others are watching the front, and Drones are at the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do now is wait for him to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So is this like a modern-day masquerade?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't these guys feel uneasy, cooped up in such a small place
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,without knowing who the others really are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't participate in social networks if you're afraid of anonymity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't virtual.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone gets hit, they'll bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A single knife can take a life away. This is the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, they don't even know who's right next to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be out of their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of thinking is why your Psycho-Pass is so cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I'm sorry. I didn't mean to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's hard to argue with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't aim at him from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The other partygoers are in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try getting closer to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suppression System, online.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.82,0:17:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mido? You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A Dominator has been detected on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a detective in there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So it really was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn Spooky Boogie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust you'll be making your escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't afford for you to be captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have unfinished business too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.55,0:18:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All the Holo-Cosplays were hacked simultaneously!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The real suspect will escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Let's use our Dominators!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Find the suspect by checking their Crime Coefficients!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The cops are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crime Coefficient is over by 110.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over by 140. He's a target for enforcement action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.53,0:18:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How many of them are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So we ended up conducting a raid, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. They got us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.38,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What was up with today's meet-up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.93,0:19:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My boyfriend got captured by the Bureau!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Everyone, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a raid by the Bureau!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I had nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not lie, Spooky Boogie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When the commotion started, they were already inside Exoset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but think that the organizer had guided them from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You've preached anarchism all this time and been admired for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, you've acted as an agent for the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a thing is impermissible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who did something to catch the Bureau's eyes in the first place, Talisman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have betrayed your own character.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You are no longer Spooky Boogie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.69,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You are no longer qualified to be an avatar admired by the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't talk like you know everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know more about you than you yourself do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's with him? He's super creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell does he think he is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to block his access.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let him in my CommuField ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you won't ever be Spooky Boogie again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman was ill-suited to the role of Spooky Boogie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But Spooky Boogie should not disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She must continue to bring smiles to everyone's faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Spooky Boogie shall remain in this world, but the woman behind her will disappear without a trace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can play a perfect Spooky Boogie, better than Sugawara Shouko herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as you became a perfect Talisman, better than Hayama Kimihiko.{kotomine kirei has made his appearance, i see}
