Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.74,0:21:50.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,900)\blur1\alpha&HFF&}It seems {\alpha&H00&}all fairy tales are dead
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:55.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}In a hospital ward of brick stones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:22:00.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,900)\blur1}my voice is too coarse to sing
